The average price of a 5kg and 12.5kg Liquefied Petroleum Gas (LPG) popularly known as cooking gas declined month-on-month by 3.03 per cent and 1.84 per cent respectively in March, 2018 a report released by the National Bureau of Statistics (NBS) on 11th April, 2018 revealed. The average price of refilling a 5kg cylinder was N2,090.6…